    "plain_content":  "A lot has been happening here at *Needle + Tech*. See our favorite branding and digital content projects from this summer.\n\nView Our Portfolio\n\nJuly 06, 2019\n\n*Make your mark:* Successful projects start with a defined vision. See how the Needle + Tech team kicked off an amazing campaign with Be The Cause.\n\nJuly 08, 2019\n\n*Guest Speaker Series:* Meet John Peace and listen to his journey as a developer for Orange.\n\nRSVP Now! ( http://www.google.com )\n\nHow did Brown Bag Pack lunch go from a local nonprofit to a growing organization that\u0027s bringing healthy lunches to students across the country?\n\nCheck out the new website and rebranding work to find out!\n\nView Case Study\n\n( http://www.facebook.com ) ( http://www.facebook.com ) ( http://www.facebook.com ) ( www.facebook.com )\n\nWe want to work on your next idea. Contact us! ( http://www.google.com )\n\n{{Sender_Name}}\n\n{{Sender_Address}} , {{Sender_City}} , {{Sender_State}} {{Sender_Zip}}\n\nUnsubscribe ( {{{unsubscribe}}} ) - Unsubscribe Preferences ( {{{unsubscribe_preferences}}} )\n\n♥ POWERED BY TWILIO SENDGRID ( https://www.sendgrid.com/?utm_source=powered-by\u0026utm_medium=email )",
